}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 317}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic And Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a long-standing commitment to sports and a belief that no journey is taken alone, Toyota is once again behind more than 200 Olympic and Paralympic athletes around the world.\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota\", \"score\": 0.9997157391340087, \"rank\": 0.0002580415251616422, \"text\": \"Toyota\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long-standing commitment\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"a belief\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"no journey\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 429}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 200 Olympic and Paralympic athletes\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 519}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The global \\\"Start Your Impossible\\\" campaign not only showcases how remarkable these athletes are but also highlights the power of local communities rallying behind them, from the coaches and teammates to parents and fans.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your Impossible\\\" campaign\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"these athletes\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"the power\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 664}, {\"ngram\": \"local communities\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"the coaches\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"teammates\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"parents\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the 2024 campaign, Toyota aspires to ignite the spark of endless possibilities within communities all over the globe.\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 783, \"end\": 789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota\", \"score\": 0.9997157391340087, \"rank\": 0.0002580415251616422, \"text\": \"Toyota\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 campaign\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"the spark\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 817}, {\"ngram\": \"endless possibilities\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 842}, {\"ngram\": \"communities\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Commercials driving the campaign include \\\"Send Off\\\", which highlights the impact of communities joining together to support their athletes; \\\"Together Wins\\\", which showcases how, together, we can truly achieve the impossible; and \\\"All For One\\\", which reminds us that when you have your community's support, you are unstoppable.\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 1208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Commercials\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"the campaign\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"communities\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"their athletes\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"your community's support\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On a local level, Toyota South Africa Motors (TSAM) is collaborating with three exceptionalSouth African sporting heroesto join the Global Team Toyota Athletes Programme - Paralympians Puseletso Mabote and Louzanne Coetzee, along with Olympic swimmer Pieter Coetz\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res