ta\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toyota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Global Team Toyota Athletes\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"various countries\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"values\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"challenge\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1641}, {\"ngram\": \"continuous improvement\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"sincerity\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"teamwork\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"humility\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"gratitude\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"accountability\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"honesty\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was introduced to track and field at a very young age when I was given my first prosthetic blade.\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very young age\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"my first prosthetic blade\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was the point where I realised my talent, and I grew to love the sport,' says Puseletso, a decorated Paralympian (T63 athlete: 100m, 200m and long jump), who has overcome challenges with grace and determination and is aiming for gold in Paris.\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1945, \"end\": 1956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2081, \"end\": 2086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999595275, \"rank\": 4.03004269853658e-1